WEBVTT

00:00:11.524 --> 00:00:13.160
(In the Southern Song, the Meis of Lin'an
got rich as seafaring merchants.)

00:00:13.184 --> 00:00:14.472
(Mei Ruohua, the Meis' spoiled daughter,
had her blissful childhood end at ten)

00:00:14.496 --> 00:00:17.656
(when Qiu Yunhai destroyed her family.
(Sold to a brothel, her suffering began.)

00:00:28.079 --> 00:00:29.079
(Ruohua.)

00:00:29.280 --> 00:00:30.280
(I'm right here.)

00:00:31.040 --> 00:00:32.016
Mother.

00:00:32.040 --> 00:00:33.055
Miss.

00:00:33.079 --> 00:00:34.119
- Ruohua.
- Miss.

00:00:34.479 --> 00:00:35.536
Over here, Miss.

00:00:35.560 --> 00:00:36.799
You can't catch me.

00:00:37.240 --> 00:00:38.240
Over here.

00:00:38.912 --> 00:00:39.735
Ruohua.

00:00:39.759 --> 00:00:40.759
Over here.

00:00:40.799 --> 00:00:41.799
Ruohua.

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:43.960
Mother.

00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:48.079
I caught you.

00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:50.840
Ruohua.

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:52.640
(Mr. Mei, Qiu Yunhai)
Greet Mr. Qiu Yunhai.

00:00:53.439 --> 00:00:55.159
(Young Mei Ruohua)
May you be well, Mr. Qiu.

00:00:56.280 --> 00:00:57.217
(Ruohua.)

00:00:57.241 --> 00:00:58.640
(Didn't you say that)

00:00:58.840 --> 00:00:59.960
(you had missed him?)

00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:01.415
He came back to celebrate

00:01:01.439 --> 00:01:02.439
your birthday.

00:01:02.719 --> 00:01:03.719
Mr. Qiu has become.

00:01:03.799 --> 00:01:04.616
(Mrs. Mei) our chief

00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:05.640
business manager.

00:01:05.799 --> 00:01:06.640
Thanks to him,

00:01:06.760 --> 00:01:07.920
our family business

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:09.096
has gained momentum

00:01:09.120 --> 00:01:10.120
and made a fortune.

00:01:11.599 --> 00:01:12.599
Miss Mei,

00:01:12.719 --> 00:01:13.719
happy birthday.

00:01:14.040 --> 00:01:15.120
Thank you, Mr. Qiu.

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:17.560
Here.

00:01:18.799 --> 00:01:19.775
It's also

00:01:19.799 --> 00:01:20.799
the Mid-Autumn Festival.

00:01:21.120 --> 00:01:22.536
Stay over tonight.

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:23.656
Yay!

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:24.680
Thank you, sir.

00:01:24.719 --> 00:01:25.719
Rest well

00:01:25.760 --> 00:01:26.960
- and drink with us.
- Alright.

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:28.079
(I'll also)

00:01:28.120 --> 00:01:29.439
Drink with you, Father.

00:01:29.799 --> 00:01:30.737
Alright.

00:01:30.761 --> 00:01:32.359
The birthday girl calls the shots.

00:01:47.876 --> 00:01:49.600
(The Legend of Heroes)

00:03:08.644 --> 00:03:09.391
=Duel on Mount Hua=

00:03:09.415 --> 00:03:11.756
(Adapted from Jin Yong's novel,
The Legend of the Condor Heroes)

00:03:11.780 --> 00:03:14.688
=Nine Yin True Sutra= =Episode 1=.

00:03:18.400 --> 00:03:19.400
Move.

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:22.000
Hurry up.

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:26.719
What are you waiting for?

00:03:30.719 --> 00:03:31.537
Legends say

00:03:31.561 --> 00:03:33.360
those who obtain the Nine Yin True Sutra

00:03:33.439 --> 00:03:35.080
become invincible.

00:03:35.919 --> 00:03:37.800
Decades after Huang Chang's death,

00:03:38.199 --> 00:03:40.840
the Nine Yin True Sutra resurfaced,

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:42.960
stirring up the martial world,

00:03:43.199 --> 00:03:45.800
causing countless casualties.

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:48.015
Therefore,

00:03:48.039 --> 00:03:50.280
the top five martial artists,

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.000
Huang Yaoshi,

00:03:52.240 --> 00:03:53.248
Ouyang Feng,

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:54.520
Duan Zhixing,

00:03:54.759 --> 00:03:55.776
Hong Qi,

00:03:55.960 --> 00:03:56.960
and Wang Chongyang.

00:03:57.400 --> 00:04:00.175
(Qunfang Pavilion)
gathered at Mount Hua's peak

00:04:00.199 --> 00:04:01.599
for a martial arts contest

00:04:01.960 --> 00:04:03.039
to stop this carnage.

00:04:03.392 --> 00:04:04.296
In the end,

00:04:04.320 --> 00:04:05.759
Wang Chongyang prevailed

00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:07.520
and obtained

00:04:08.039 --> 00:04:09.520
the Nine Yin True Sutra.

00:04:10.759 --> 00:04:11.960
Nine Yin True Sutra.

00:04:14.080 --> 00:04:15.360
Path to invincibility.

00:04:15.639 --> 00:04:16.720
None of your business.

00:04:17.088 --> 00:04:18.056
Move.

00:04:18.080 --> 00:04:19.279
Stop hitting her.

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:20.600
Let me warn you.

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:22.457
If you damage

00:04:22.481 --> 00:04:23.519
her pretty face,

00:04:24.040 --> 00:04:25.040
I'll kill you.

00:04:26.600 --> 00:04:27.600
Come on. Let's go.

00:04:27.872 --> 00:04:28.816
Slowly.

00:04:28.840 --> 00:04:30.319
Emperor Duan Zhixing of Dali

00:04:30.439 --> 00:04:31.439
Mei Ruohua.

00:04:31.800 --> 00:04:32.777
Today

00:04:32.801 --> 00:04:33.920
is a good day.

00:04:34.304 --> 00:04:35.295
I have

00:04:35.319 --> 00:04:37.439
found you a good client,

00:04:37.920 --> 00:04:39.279
an old acquaintance of yours.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:41.959
Behave

00:04:42.079 --> 00:04:43.439
and serve him well.

00:04:43.808 --> 00:04:44.736
Then

00:04:44.760 --> 00:04:46.920
everyone will be happy.

00:04:47.199 --> 00:04:48.480
Otherwise,

00:04:48.959 --> 00:04:51.120
I won't go easy on you.

00:04:53.759 --> 00:04:55.600
Well, better not wear it.

00:04:56.319 --> 00:04:57.839
There would be trouble

00:04:58.040 --> 00:04:59.199
if it hurts the guest.

00:05:01.959 --> 00:05:03.560
Drink by yourself.

00:05:03.872 --> 00:05:04.855
Alright.

00:05:04.879 --> 00:05:05.879
Go.

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:07.657
Sir.

00:05:07.681 --> 00:05:09.160
Let me toast you.

00:05:30.404 --> 00:05:32.055
(Mei Ruohua)

00:05:32.079 --> 00:05:33.079
Sir.

00:05:37.279 --> 00:05:38.639
Qiu Yunhai.

00:05:53.959 --> 00:05:54.976
Mei Ruohua.

00:06:00.240 --> 00:06:01.639
This place suits you well.

00:06:04.680 --> 00:06:05.879
It's been a decade, huh?

00:06:06.639 --> 00:06:07.639
More or less.

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:14.120
If your father could see

00:06:15.240 --> 00:06:17.360
what you've become from the after world,

00:06:17.639 --> 00:06:18.759
he'd be heartbroken.

00:06:18.944 --> 00:06:19.855
Shameless.

00:06:19.879 --> 00:06:20.879
You...

00:06:25.079 --> 00:06:26.079
Suffer for the rest

00:06:26.360 --> 00:06:27.360
of your life.

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:34.160
Scared I'll kill you?

00:06:41.120 --> 00:06:42.120
I'm waiting.

00:06:45.760 --> 00:06:46.697
Sir.

00:06:46.721 --> 00:06:47.959
Madam sends you the new girl

00:06:48.040 --> 00:06:49.240
as a kind gesture.

00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:52.680
She's filthy.

00:06:53.040 --> 00:06:54.040
You like her?

00:06:54.439 --> 00:06:55.439
She's yours.

00:07:00.399 --> 00:07:01.639
You're so lucky.

00:07:12.576 --> 00:07:13.536
Hey, pretty.

00:07:13.560 --> 00:07:14.560
Relax.

00:07:14.759 --> 00:07:15.759
I'll be gentle.

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:17.279
I won't hurt you.

00:07:23.480 --> 00:07:24.560
Trying to run?

00:07:31.439 --> 00:07:32.439
Get lost.

00:07:34.079 --> 00:07:35.079
Let go.

00:08:31.920 --> 00:08:32.928
Keep her alive.

00:08:54.799 --> 00:08:55.799
Keep running.

00:08:59.240 --> 00:09:00.240
Get her.

00:09:17.472 --> 00:09:18.456
Get her.

00:09:18.480 --> 00:09:19.520
- Understood!
- Understood!

00:09:24.679 --> 00:09:25.679
- Get her!
- Get her!

00:09:51.960 --> 00:09:52.960
Wait.

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:01.240
Have you seen a woman in red?

00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:02.840
No.

00:10:07.720 --> 00:10:08.720
No?

00:10:53.879 --> 00:10:54.880
Come on out.

00:11:10.080 --> 00:11:11.080
Thank you.

00:11:11.460 --> 00:11:12.480
Yah!

00:12:26.039 --> 00:12:27.039
She's right inside.

00:12:27.879 --> 00:12:29.159
Search thoroughly.

00:12:30.080 --> 00:12:31.136
I want her alive.

00:12:32.440 --> 00:12:33.480
You scheming viper!

00:12:33.879 --> 00:12:34.879
I'll kill you!

00:12:51.919 --> 00:12:52.832
Over there.

00:12:52.919 --> 00:12:53.736
Get her.

00:12:53.760 --> 00:12:54.615
Hurry.

00:12:54.639 --> 00:12:55.639
Get her.

00:12:56.928 --> 00:12:57.928
Hurry.

00:13:00.080 --> 00:13:01.080
Over here.

00:13:02.080 --> 00:13:03.080
Hurry.

00:13:15.759 --> 00:13:16.759
Hurry.

00:13:37.600 --> 00:13:38.600
Go.

00:13:45.476 --> 00:13:47.584
(Master of Taohua Island, Huang Yaoshi)

00:14:21.879 --> 00:14:23.039
I've never seen anyone

00:14:23.320 --> 00:14:24.399
with your martial skills.

00:14:24.799 --> 00:14:26.159
Please take me as your disciple.

00:14:40.000 --> 00:14:41.000
Please rise.

00:14:45.639 --> 00:14:46.960
I'll teach you three moves.

00:14:49.960 --> 00:14:50.960
Watch closely.

00:14:51.519 --> 00:14:52.759
I'm only showing you once.

00:15:21.559 --> 00:15:22.559
Got it?

00:15:22.759 --> 00:15:23.759
I

00:15:24.519 --> 00:15:25.720
I hope my inner energy

00:15:26.399 --> 00:15:28.519
can help you get what you want.

00:15:51.908 --> 00:15:53.440
(Qunfang Pavilion)

00:16:01.080 --> 00:16:02.080
You dare

00:16:02.320 --> 00:16:03.456
to show up again?

00:16:07.399 --> 00:16:08.440
Qiu Yunhai.

00:16:10.720 --> 00:16:11.720
Come out.

00:16:11.840 --> 00:16:12.840
What's wrong?

00:16:14.799 --> 00:16:15.919
It's you.

00:16:16.519 --> 00:16:18.039
You're asking for this.

00:16:18.360 --> 00:16:20.360
I won't go easy on you.

00:16:36.200 --> 00:16:37.200
You've learned

00:16:37.799 --> 00:16:38.799
a few moves, huh?

00:16:39.399 --> 00:16:40.399
Get her!

00:16:57.508 --> 00:16:58.560
(Qunfang Pavilion)

00:17:11.160 --> 00:17:12.160
Beat her.

00:17:13.599 --> 00:17:15.119
That's brutal.

00:17:15.880 --> 00:17:17.279
Poor young lady.

00:17:17.536 --> 00:17:18.457
Indeed.

00:17:18.481 --> 00:17:19.520
Enough.

00:17:21.240 --> 00:17:22.680
Don't be so harsh.

00:17:27.319 --> 00:17:28.352
Get up.

00:17:28.880 --> 00:17:29.920
Look at you.

00:17:30.680 --> 00:17:32.095
I thought you became

00:17:32.119 --> 00:17:33.240
a martial artist overnight.

00:17:37.559 --> 00:17:38.616
You're staring at me?

00:17:38.640 --> 00:17:39.744
Stop!

00:17:45.184 --> 00:17:46.119
Who is she?

00:17:46.200 --> 00:17:47.136
Who is she?

00:17:47.160 --> 00:17:48.160
No idea.

00:17:50.016 --> 00:17:52.696
(Madam of Taohua Island, Feng Heng)
Bully a woman in broad daylight.

00:17:52.960 --> 00:17:53.960
Have you no shame?

00:18:00.960 --> 00:18:02.200
Fine, I can stop.

00:18:06.720 --> 00:18:08.799
If you trade places with her.

00:18:16.119 --> 00:18:17.319
I know how to

00:18:17.480 --> 00:18:18.799
treat a lady properly.

00:18:23.839 --> 00:18:24.896
Nice aroma.

00:18:27.400 --> 00:18:28.960
With your stunning looks,

00:18:29.240 --> 00:18:31.200
I'll treat you right, my fair lady.

00:18:33.572 --> 00:18:35.176
(Qunfang Pavilion)

00:18:35.200 --> 00:18:36.440
She's got some fight in her.

00:18:38.000 --> 00:18:39.920
I enjoy taming wild horses.

00:18:42.212 --> 00:18:43.212
(Taohua Island, Hong)

00:18:45.440 --> 00:18:46.440
My blade.

00:18:52.960 --> 00:18:54.599
You'll be fine. Don't be scared.

00:19:18.599 --> 00:19:19.648
Are you alright?

00:19:20.640 --> 00:19:21.640
I'm okay.

00:19:24.519 --> 00:19:25.519
Let's go then.

00:19:26.200 --> 00:19:27.200
Wait.

00:19:28.319 --> 00:19:29.319
Come with us.

00:19:34.480 --> 00:19:35.480
Come on.

00:20:54.119 --> 00:20:55.040
Master.

00:20:55.119 --> 00:20:56.200
It's not sustainable...

00:20:59.880 --> 00:21:00.799
It's not sustainable

00:21:00.880 --> 00:21:02.039
for you to help my lady

00:21:02.640 --> 00:21:03.880
resist the cold poison.

00:21:05.680 --> 00:21:06.680
Is the Solar Mantra

00:21:06.880 --> 00:21:08.255
incompatible with your original

00:21:08.279 --> 00:21:09.279
cultivation?

00:21:10.440 --> 00:21:11.296
The Ninefold Yin Pill

00:21:11.320 --> 00:21:12.680
doesn't allow my lady

00:21:12.960 --> 00:21:14.039
to develop yang energy.

00:21:14.519 --> 00:21:16.095
You have to keep transferring

00:21:16.119 --> 00:21:17.176
yang energy to her

00:21:17.200 --> 00:21:18.200
via the Solar Mantra.

00:21:18.839 --> 00:21:20.160
But it's only temporary.

00:21:20.440 --> 00:21:21.416
You may risk

00:21:21.440 --> 00:21:22.417
losing control

00:21:22.441 --> 00:21:23.480
I'm well aware.

00:21:25.039 --> 00:21:26.519
But what else can I do?

00:21:33.792 --> 00:21:34.792
Please

00:21:34.960 --> 00:21:35.960
take me in.

00:21:38.160 --> 00:21:39.160
Get up, Miss.

00:21:39.640 --> 00:21:41.200
Bad people killed my entire family.

00:21:41.920 --> 00:21:43.240
I'm the sole survivor.

00:21:44.039 --> 00:21:45.279
I must master martial arts

00:21:45.759 --> 00:21:46.759
to avenge my family.

00:21:50.119 --> 00:21:51.119
Please

00:21:51.400 --> 00:21:52.400
take me as your disciple.

00:21:53.640 --> 00:21:54.720
Are you done?

00:21:57.960 --> 00:21:58.960
Yes.

00:22:08.920 --> 00:22:09.960
All beings suffer.

00:22:11.920 --> 00:22:13.079
I feel for you,

00:22:15.160 --> 00:22:16.759
but I can't take you in.

00:22:21.480 --> 00:22:22.480
You should go.

00:22:23.640 --> 00:22:24.640
Yaoshi.

00:22:38.119 --> 00:22:39.559
Is it the girl we met?

00:22:41.240 --> 00:22:42.559
She wants to be your disciple?

00:22:44.759 --> 00:22:45.759
You rejected her?

00:22:54.039 --> 00:22:55.640
The world overflows with misery.

00:22:56.920 --> 00:22:57.920
We can't save everyone.

00:22:59.640 --> 00:23:00.640
That's true.

00:23:01.079 --> 00:23:02.319
We've seen so many people

00:23:03.119 --> 00:23:04.279
and gone through so much.

00:23:05.200 --> 00:23:06.920
We're leaves wavering in the wind.

00:23:08.880 --> 00:23:10.720
Of course, I'm among the fortunate ones.

00:23:14.319 --> 00:23:15.759
When danger struck,

00:23:16.160 --> 00:23:18.000
she risked everything to protect me.

00:23:18.839 --> 00:23:20.359
That was deeply moving.

00:23:24.119 --> 00:23:25.119
You spend

00:23:25.559 --> 00:23:27.319
half the year in secluded cultivation.

00:23:28.880 --> 00:23:30.400
She's around my age.

00:23:31.519 --> 00:23:33.039
If she joined us on the island,

00:23:33.519 --> 00:23:34.519
I would

00:23:34.640 --> 00:23:35.815
have one more person

00:23:35.839 --> 00:23:36.920
to talk to.

00:23:37.559 --> 00:23:38.559
My Lady.

00:23:40.920 --> 00:23:41.920
Fine.

00:23:43.720 --> 00:23:45.400
I know you well.

00:23:48.240 --> 00:23:49.280
Forget it.

00:24:09.124 --> 00:24:11.232
(Yunhai Manor)

00:24:13.119 --> 00:24:14.400
I failed the task.

00:24:21.400 --> 00:24:22.400
Sir.

00:24:22.799 --> 00:24:24.480
I deserve the worst punishment.

00:24:31.480 --> 00:24:32.480
Sir.

00:24:34.119 --> 00:24:35.119
Sir.

00:24:36.000 --> 00:24:37.000
Get up.

00:24:46.359 --> 00:24:47.359
You know?

00:24:47.960 --> 00:24:48.992
That man

00:24:49.319 --> 00:24:50.440
was Huang Yaoshi,

00:24:51.079 --> 00:24:52.519
one of the Five Greats

00:24:52.759 --> 00:24:53.960
from the duel on Mount Hua.

00:24:54.599 --> 00:24:55.735
How did he know

00:24:55.759 --> 00:24:56.759
Mei Ruohua?

00:25:00.160 --> 00:25:01.279
I have no idea.

00:25:03.319 --> 00:25:04.319
(So you're saying)

00:25:04.759 --> 00:25:06.400
(the man we saw was Huang Yaoshi?)

00:25:06.799 --> 00:25:07.920
(I saw him cough up blood.)

00:25:08.119 --> 00:25:09.119
He must be injured.

00:25:11.599 --> 00:25:12.640
Qiao Si.

00:25:14.480 --> 00:25:15.480
Track him down

00:25:16.440 --> 00:25:17.440
and kill him.

00:25:18.519 --> 00:25:19.519
Sir.

00:25:20.319 --> 00:25:21.680
He's Huang Yaoshi.

00:25:21.960 --> 00:25:23.200
But he's weak right now.

00:25:24.160 --> 00:25:25.160
Kill him

00:25:25.319 --> 00:25:26.640
and we will be famous.

00:25:43.359 --> 00:25:44.359
This flower

00:25:44.759 --> 00:25:45.759
blooms so well.

00:25:47.279 --> 00:25:48.440
Not as pretty as you.

00:25:50.799 --> 00:25:51.799
Yaoshi.

00:25:54.119 --> 00:25:55.640
Honestly, I can relate

00:25:56.480 --> 00:25:57.680
to this orchid.

00:25:58.559 --> 00:26:00.240
I have no regrets after blooming

00:26:01.920 --> 00:26:02.960
in full glory.

00:26:06.119 --> 00:26:07.160
Don't be silly.

00:26:08.480 --> 00:26:09.559
Meeting you has been

00:26:11.160 --> 00:26:13.119
the greatest pleasure in my life.

00:26:15.960 --> 00:26:16.960
I promise

00:26:17.599 --> 00:26:19.119
everything will be alright.

00:26:24.200 --> 00:26:26.480
I don't want to watch the sunrise
at Mount Tai anymore.

00:26:30.079 --> 00:26:31.264
I'm tired.

00:26:34.319 --> 00:26:35.319
Let's go home.

00:26:38.559 --> 00:26:39.575
Master.

00:26:39.599 --> 00:26:41.079
She's still kneeling outside.

00:26:49.124 --> 00:26:50.496
(Auspicious Blessings)

00:27:11.204 --> 00:27:12.832
(Auspicious Blessings)

00:27:49.720 --> 00:27:51.119
He's no longer dangerous.

00:27:51.599 --> 00:27:52.720
Whoever kills him

00:27:53.039 --> 00:27:54.279
will rise to fame overnight.

